Class Ground

java.lang.Object
  fr.imac.javawars.engine.Ground

public class Ground
extends java.lang.Object

Class Map : create map with : image (gif or png), xml file or random * * * Image map Wall : Black Path : White Neutral Bases : Grey Players' Bases : 4 distincts colors (with R, G & B differents) * * * Legends XML Wall --> -2 Path --> -1 Neutral Bases --> 0 Players' Bases --> >= 1
